OL,6,FA minister who defrauded his church of
OL,7,F#10,000 and a grieving parishioner of
OL,8,F#1,000 has been jailed for six months.
OL,10,FAs he sent Adrian Robert McLaughlin to
OL,11,Fprison, Judge Patrick Lynch KC told
OL,12,Fthe now former reverend that he abused
OL,13,Fthe trust of his congregation and
OL,14,Fregarded the parish "as if it was a
OL,15,Fpersonal fiefdom".
OL,17,FThe 50-year-old father of two was
OL,18,Fconvicted by a jury of defrauding
OL,19,F#10,000 from St Coleman's Parish
OL,20,FChurch in Dunmurry on a date between
OL,21,FOctober 15 and November 30, 2016.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
