OL,6,FBefore imposing the term, Judge Lynch,
OL,7,Fwho was sitting in Belfast Crown
OL,8,FCourt, outlined McLaughlin's offending.
OL,10,FHe revealed that McLaughlin, from
OL,11,FChurch Avenue in Dunmurry, had been
OL,12,Fthe minister of St Coleman's Church of
OL,13,FIreland since 2014.
OL,15,FIn January 2016 a fire at the church
OL,16,Fcaused extensive damage and a fund was
OL,17,Fset up to help with the restoration
OL,18,Fcosts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
