OL,6,FShe made the donation on the
OL,7,Funderstanding that the money would be
OL,8,Fused to purchase memorial items in
OL,9,Fhonour of her deceased husband which
OL,10,Fwere to be positioned in the church.
OL,12,FOn this occasion, McLaughlin requested
OL,13,Fthat the payee line be left blank -
OL,14,Fand instead of purchasing the memorial
OL,15,Fitem McLaughlin filled in his own name
OL,16,Fand pocketed the #1,000.
OL,18,FDespite the offences being committed
OL,19,Fin 2016, they were not detected until
OL,20,F2018 and McLaughlin was interviewed by
OL,21,Fthe PSNI in 2020.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
