OL,6,FRegarding the widow, in her statement
OL,7,Fshe spoke of her "upset" at being lied
OL,8,Fto by McLaughlin who she said was
OL,9,F"someone my late husband and I
OL,10,Ftrusted".
OL,12,FThe judge commented: "The sense of
OL,13,Fhurt and disappointment oozed from
OL,14,Fevery sentence of her statement."
OL,16,FIn his statement, the parishioner who
OL,17,Fco-signed the #10,000 cheque said the
OL,18,Fallegations of fraud and McLaughlin's
OL,19,Factions resulted in him and his family
OL,20,Fleaving St Coleman's in November 2019.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
