OL,6,FHe said: "After a life-time of
OL,7,Fbelonging to the community of St
OL,8,FColeman's, this is a huge wrench for
OL,9,Fall of us and it's still sometimes
OL,10,Fdifficult for me to believe this has
OL,11,Fhappened."
OL,13,FPrior to passing sentence, Judge Lynch
OL,14,Fsaid he had taken into consideration
OL,15,Fdefence submissions made by Richard
OL,16,FMcConkey KC.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
