OL,6,FThese included the delay in bringing
OL,7,Fthe case to court, the impact and
OL,8,Fhardship a prison sentence would have
OL,9,Fon McLaughlin's two children and his
OL,10,Fprevious good character.
OL,12,FJudge Lynch said it was "frequently
OL,13,Fand unfortunately the case" that
OL,14,Frelatives of criminals "suffer as much
OL,15,For even more" as the offender - but
OL,16,Fthat this "has to be balanced against
OL,17,Fthe harm done."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
